javax.ws.rs.ext
Interface MessageBodyHandlerContext<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Java type supported by corresponding message body provider
All Superinterfaces:
BaseContext
All Known Subinterfaces:
ReadFromHandlerContext<T>, WriteToHandlerContext<T>
public interface MessageBodyHandlerContext<T>
extends BaseContext

Context shared by handlers. Handlers can be used to intercept calls to javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyReader.readFrom and javax.ws.rs.ext.MessageBodyWriter.writeTo. The getters and setters in this context class correspond to the parameters in the aforementioned methods.

Since:
2.0
Author:
Santiago Pericas-Geertsen, Bill Burke
See Also:
ReadFromHandler, WriteToHandler
